import React from 'react'

import { SocialMediaIconsReact } from 'social-media-icons-react'

export const TwitterIcon = () => (
  <SocialMediaIconsReact 
    icon="twitter" 
    url="https://twitter.com/tinashe_88"
    iconColor="rgba(28,186,223,1)" 
    iconSize="5" 
    roundness="20%" 
    size="100"
    backgroundColor=""
  />
)

export const InstagramIcon = () => (
  <SocialMediaIconsReact
    icon="instagram" 
    url="https://instagram.com/tinashe88"
    iconColor="rgba(193, 53, 132, 1)" 
    iconSize="5" 
    roundness="20%" 
    size="100"
    backgroundColor=""
  />
)

export const GithubIcon = () => (
  <SocialMediaIconsReact 
    icon="github" 
    url="https://github.com/tinashe-88"
    iconColor="rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)" 
    backgroundColor=""
    iconSize="5" 
    roundness="20%" 
    size="100"
  />
)
